t I can't verify that without more information.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Status report compiled but delivery timed out — target Lead session is awaiting response. Compiling final report for this cron session output:\\n\\n---\\n\\n**🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 19:26 UTC 14 Apr**\\n\\n**Active sessions: 4**\\n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status → Lead): **running** — This status report cron — ~1m\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (5p QLHV Progress): **running** — Ecosystem health monitor — ~1h 35m\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (5p DTLX Progress): **running** — DTLX health monitor — ~1h 42m\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` (QLHV Ecosystem): **running** — Group monitoring / standby — ~3h 18m\\n\\n**Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅** | MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅ | No blockers. No revert loopbacks.\\n\\n⚠️ Delivery to Lead (`telegram:direct:6053576134`) timed out — target session appears to be awaiting agent response.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 181,\n            \"output\": 453,\n            \"totalTokens\": 22177,\n            \"cacheRead\": 20376,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 1167,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776194882603,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dc843f01161b4101f84f572276f35\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"68175aba\",\n            \"seq\": 8\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n        \"to